--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
INFORMATION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This file lists changes made to the Ansible role. It follows semantic versioning
guidelines. The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and formatted
to allow easy grepping by scripts.

The fields are:
B: bug
C: change
E: enhancement
F: feature

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Version 1.3.1 (2020-11-27)
E: Improve Monit configuration file

* Version 1.3.0 (2020-11-24)
F: Add support for Monit service monitoring (squid_monitor_monit_state)

* Version 1.2.2 (2020-10-30)
E: Simplify Ansible file header (ansible_managed)

* Version 1.2.1 (2020-01-08)
B: Minor Jinja2 statement fix

* Version 1.2.0 (2019-09-27)
F: Add support for CentOS 8

* Version 1.1.0 (2019-05-26)
F: Port role to Ansible 2.8

* Version 1.0.1 (2018-12-19)
B: Fix 'path' parameter in 'squid_cache_dir' option

* Version 1.0.0 (2018-12-12)
E: Mark Ansible role as 'stable'
E: Minor style improvement

* Version 0.2.0 (2018-10-18)
F: Add support for 'SSL_ports' option (squid_acl_ssl_ports)

* Version 0.1.2 (2018-09-15)
B: Correct location of 'file_dst_cache_dir'

* Version 0.1.1 (2018-09-14)
E: Add 'no_log' parameter to sensitive tasks

* Version 0.1.0 (2018-09-02)
F: Initial release
